cs.CR, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.IT, cs.DS

The paper discusses attacks on the smart grid, which is a cyber-physical system. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves optimization and decision-making, which suggests that it could belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions mutual information and Kullback-Leibler divergence, which are concepts from information theory, indicating that it could belong to cs.IT (Information Theory). Finally, the paper involves numerical assessments, which suggests that it could belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
